                        p.lead
                            | A Point of Sale (POS) system helps your business to accept customer payments and monitor sales, including trends. The POS setup varies based on whether you operate online,have an offline brick-and-mortar store, or both. It offers you advanced capabilities such as inventory management, sales performance tracking, staff management, customer contact information collection, and various other functionalities.
